      "content": "rest? i dont know if i've been resting. it feels more like i'm just haunting my own life. everything is just so heavy and meaningless now. it feels like the \"rest\" you're talking about is the only thing that actually makes sense anymore. like, why keep the machinery running if the person is already gone?",
